":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3274131f648fa5128d5a8f799ce0a531a0ead2ba","tid":1969000,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"講咗幾多次<br />\n點解Twitter 文宣最有效呀? <br />\n<br />\n因為調查記者全部都鐘意用Twitter 揾料呀!! 同普通網民文宣緊要，定同人地啲記者文宣緊要呀? 人地喺自己國家寫一句好過你喺Reddit推十個post<br />\n<br />\nReddit 連登個search 廢到一個點，Facebook Youtube 要本身識去邊個page 先睇到香港片。Twitter 只要夠多人一齊用同一個hashtag 出post，個hashtag 就自動上每日trending hashtag list，人人都會喺homepage 右手邊見到 #HongKongProtest<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgr9XVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffgr9XVL.png&h=6153e74f&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以Twitter要人!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再教你用記者偏愛Twitter嘅最大原因--Tweetdeck，輕鬆收風<br />\n1. 開Twitter 帳號 + 喺電腦登入<br />\n2.  去 <a href=\"https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftweetdeck.twitter.com%2F&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=8a1c56f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/</a> ，會見到下面網頁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A490kcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA490kcb.png&h=4c988f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTweetdeck每一列等於一個搜尋結果，最重要係每一列都會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自動更新</strong></span></span>。列1至列三都係搜尋關鍵字同hashtags，列寧就特別啲，係搜尋一組自訂嘅用戶嘅動態，要新增就要撳左手邊深藍色工具列個箭嘴，會出咗: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhkyFfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhkyFfw.png&h=33693218&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n撳&quot;List&quot;，就會俾你㨂列寧要follow邊個用戶。<br />\n<br />\n所以連登仔們，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乖啦! 用Twitter啦! </span></strong></span><br />\n真係求你地，唔洗淨用Twitter，但係起碼得閒去Twitter開個post幫手推hashtag"}}